Not all crafting materials are on the surface - some may require you to dig underground or into a mountain.

§7§oA §epickaxe§f helps you uncover all sorts of materials, such as stone, coal, iron and precious ore - though you may need extra sturdy tools for some rare materials!

Some raw metals will need to be smelted using a §efurnace§f. Place a fuel like coal or wood logs in the fuel slot, then add raw ore to smelt it into something useful.